plot: When Lamar suggests he and Khloé create a unisex fragrance together, Khloé fears it will cause conflict in their relationship. As the bulk of the responsibility falls on her, she grows frustrated with Lamar and feels emotionally torn about whether she can continue to mix business with their marriage. Meanwhile, Malika starts dating Lamar's friend and fellow NBA player Rasual Butler. But when her strange relationship with Rob ends up sabotaging her new romance, she wonders if there's more between them than she'd like to admit.—Guilherme O.
